#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Metalink2"
msgstr "Membuat sebuah Metalink2"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you have to enter the &URL; from where you are trying to download the "
"file. Also you can enter some optional information such as Preference "
"(Priority) for a particular mirror if you are adding more then one mirrors, "
"for the file you want to download."
msgstr ""
"Di sini Anda harus memasukkan &URL; darimana Anda akan mengunduh filenya. "
"Juga Anda dapat memasukkan beberapa informasi secara pilihan seperti "
"Preferensi (prioritas), untuk file yang ingin Anda unduh."

